<p>8—<hi rend="underline">Yes</hi></p>
<p>9 )</p>
<p>10) difficult and will take months to answer=</p>
<p>11)</p>
<p>12. Seldom</p>
<p>13. You have beautifully expressed the Native actions</p>
<p>14— yes.</p>
<p>15— yes</p>
